Subject: [PATCH 015/456] ARM: zynq: xilinx_axidma: set default value for DMA
 Channel Coalesce

Signed-off-by: Nicolae Rosia <nicolae.rosia@certsign.ro>
Reported-by: Kedareswara rao Appana <appanad@xilinx.com>
Signed-off-by: Michal Simek <michal.simek@xilinx.com>
(cherry picked from commit 00ff5b248654d751a72265c1fad1919d6e4b2ce8)
---
 drivers/dma/xilinx/xilinx_axidma.c |    1 +
 1 files changed, 1 insertions(+), 0 deletions(-)

diff --git a/drivers/dma/xilinx/xilinx_axidma.c b/drivers/dma/xilinx/xilinx_axidma.c
index 68f5969..af7ffdb 100644
--- a/drivers/dma/xilinx/xilinx_axidma.c
+++ b/drivers/dma/xilinx/xilinx_axidma.c
@@ -888,6 +888,7 @@ static int xilinx_dma_chan_probe(struct xilinx_dma_device *xdev,
 		return -ENOMEM;
 
 	chan->max_len = XILINX_DMA_MAX_TRANS_LEN;
+	chan->config.coalesc = 0x01;
 
 	chan->has_dre = of_property_read_bool(node, "xlnx,include-dre");
 
